spanGrp.span: GAK talks about the history of the Tabaq people. He starts with advice to the new generation about the importance of language in preserving the people's culture and identity. Then he talks about the history of the Tabaq: from where they came, where they first settled, who their relatives are, and how the Tabaq migrated and settled in the area which is now known as the Tabaq area.
